review: Visited for pregnancy related . Cleanliness is very good inside clinic . All kinds of online payments accepted in the clinic. Small Pharmacy is also available in clinic.  Overall experience was very good and appreciate doctors ability and genuineness In understanding the issues across all aspects from patients point of view and suggesting relevant solutions and explaining them in greater detail. Experienced Great positivity after speaking to the Dr .  Excellent doctor . Many Many thanks to Dr. Sunitha.

review:
*** ** *** **** ************ *** ************ ** **** ******* very professional and patient friendly and highly competent and the clinic is easily accessible and in a good location. They also have a full pledged cardiology supportive services in cases pregnant women need to be screened for any cardiac problem. Also very happy with prenatal anaomaly scan and growth scan services done by experts of the field 

Overall it's a highly rated clinic. I highly recommend for Gynecological and Obstetric service
